1. *Kauču* sam kupila u prodavnici nameštaja. (I bought *a couch* at the furniture store.)
2. Ovaj *kauč* je veoma udoban. (This *couch* is very comfortable.)
3. *Kauča* nema u dnevnoj sobi. (There is no *couch* in the living room.)
4. Stavila sam jastuk na *kauč*. (I put a pillow on the *couch*.)
5. Deca vole da skakuću po *kauču*. (Children like to jump on the *couch*.)
6. *Kaučevi* u salonu su presvučeni novom tkaninom. (The *couches* in the salon have been reupholstered with new fabric.)
7. Naš *kauč* može da se pretvori u udoban krevet. (Our *couch* can turn into a comfortable bed.)
8. *Kauču* treba da stavimo novu navlaku. (We need to put a new cover on the *couch*.)
9. Sedište na *kauču* je malo izdignuto. (The seat on the *couch* is a little raised.)
10. Prostor između zida i *kauča* je mali. (The space between the wall and the *couch* is small.)